Thanks for the comments! I implemented your suggestions as well as some cleanups I'd discussed with @rxin, then benchmarked the PR on 16 m2.4xlarge machines with the uk-2007-05 web graph for 10 iterations of PageRank to make sure it didn't introduce a performance regression.

| Commit | Runtime +/- SEM |
| --- | --- |
| pre-unify-rdds (ankurdave/spark@f96ea3a02f64e6e0fec4dcb1f498c6bcde4af699) | 418 +/- 17.1 s |
